summaries.short: Conner Kent escapes from Cadmus Labs and emerges into the world for the first time as a free agent.
summaries.full: Conner Kent escapes from Cadmus Labs and emerges into the world for the first time as a free agent; his search for the truth about his past leads him to Lionel Luthor, Lex's father, and Cadmus geneticist Eve Watson, who informs him of his heritage.

summaries.short: Tensions are running high at Titans Tower following their most recent encounter with Deathstroke; Kory tries to learn more about Conner Kent; Rose tries to help Jason cope with his near-death experience.
summaries.full: Tensions are running high at Titans Tower following their most recent encounter with Deathstroke; Kory tries to learn more about Conner Kent; Rose tries to help Jason cope with his near-death experience.

summaries.short: Dick and the rest of the team vow to do everything in their power to save Jason Todd's life.
summaries.full: With the team thrown into upheaval, Dick and the rest vow to do everything in their power to save Jason Todd's life; Gar's guilt over Jason's kidnapping complicates the mission to save the fellow Titan; Rachel's dark secret continues to gnaw at her.

summaries.short: Dick finally reveals the truth to the team; the secret behind Deathstroke's vendetta.
summaries.full: Dick finally reveals the truth to the team; flashbacks reveal the secret behind Deathstroke's vendetta against the Titans; Dick, Donna, Dawn and Hank befriend Jericho Wilson, Deathstroke's son; Dick faces a choice between loyalty and revenge.

summaries.short: Four years ago, Dick, Donna, Hank, Dawn and Garth, aka Aqualad, live together in Titans Tower, thriving as a superhero team and growing into a tight-knight family, until their personal feelings start to bleed into their work.
summaries.full: Four years ago, Dick, Donna, Hank, Dawn and Garth, aka Aqualad, live together in Titans Tower, thriving as a superhero team and growing into a tight-knight family, until their personal feelings start to bleed into their work.

summaries.short: In the aftermath of Dick's confession, his fear that his secret would break the group up comes true.
summaries.full: In the aftermath of Dick's confession, the Titans' world is rocked to the core, and Dick's fear that his secret would break the group up comes true; the heroes abandon Titans Tower and go their separate ways; Faddel has returned with bad news.

summaries.short: With the re-emergence of Dr. Light, the old Titans reluctantly return to Titans Tower to strategize against their old enemy, but the secrets of the Titans' past threaten to tear the newly formed team apart from within.
summaries.full: With the re-emergence of Dr. Light, the old Titans reluctantly return to Titans Tower to strategize against their old enemy, but the secrets of the Titans' past threaten to tear the newly formed team apart from within.
